@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rvjcof(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.46
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.62)) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.85) / wp.abs(v0 + 0.56)))
    tmp = (v0 / (wp.exp(v0 + 0.65) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.55)))
    v0 = (0.39 / (v1 / v2))
    v0 = ((0.29 * v2) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.48) * (v1 + 0.08 * tmp + 0.55)))
    data[tid] = v0
